 {
    "id": 2,
    "offset": 340510,
    "slot_size": 230,
    "data_size": 226,
    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "I[SP]acted[SP]like[SP]a[SP]big[SP]hero,[SP]ordering[SP]my[SP]guys\nnot[SP]to[SP]pick[SP]on[SP]the[SP]weak...[SP]But[SP]that[SP]was[SP]all\njust[SP]a[SP]front.",
