    "data_size": 260,
    "nom_orig": "Yukino",
    "texte_orig": "Alright,[SP]time[SP]to[SP]spill[SP]it[SP]all.[SP]If[SP]you[SP]don't,\nyou're[SP]gonna[SP]find[SP]there's[SP]way[SP]worse[SP]than\ngetting[SP]your[SP]pants[SP]pulled[SP]down.",
