  {
    "id": 22,
    "offset": 344468,
    "slot_size": 280,
    "data_size": 276,
    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "Looks[SP]like[SP]you're[SP]telling[SP]the[SP]truth...[1205][001E]\nAlright,[SP]you're[SP]off[SP]the[SP]hook.[SP]But[SP]you[SP]better\nnot[SP]go[SP]near[SP]Joker[SP]ever[SP]again,[SP]got[SP]it!?",
